<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR><P ALIGN=CENTER><b>In Reply To:</b> <A HREF="http://www.everworld.net/cgi-local/pvp.cgi?read=1531" TARGET=_self>Info on PvP</A> (Elwin)
</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>I'm an ogre, named Petunia. I roleplayer him all the time. The name is a great opener for meeting people and I've become fairly well-known because of the name "You no make fun of name or me BASH!"

<BR>As for PKing, I've been in The Feerrott for two days and have yet to see a single instance of PKing. I think the people that choose to play Ogres are just generally of a maturer sort.
<P>I am having fun and am VERY VERY glad I chose the PvP server to play on. Remember this isn't UO. All the d00ds you talk about are still back in UO saying "EQ SUX!!!". Let them stay there I say. And that fact that macroing is so far impossible in EQ will keep the d00ds away in droves.
<P>Join the PvP server. You won't regret it.
<P>Holly.
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
